<div>
  <div class="relative text-center w-full min-h-[200px] md:min-h-[300px] text-neutral-content p-10 lg:p-30 ">
    <%= image_tag "background/backgroundservices.avif",
        class: "absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover",
        alt: "Background image with someone working on a computer project",
        fetchpriority: "high",
        loading: "eager" %>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 reveal delay-1">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl ">
        <%= title 'Your ideas deserve to become <span class="text-gradient">reality</span>'.html_safe %>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl p-8 md:text-center lg:text-2xl text-primary-content ">
        <%= description "and it all starts with a conversation!" %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section class="py-16 px-8 md:p-20 reveal delay-2">
    <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl  text-accent text-center mb-16">
      Our services
    </h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center mx-8 md:mx-20 gap-8 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1 w-full md:text-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <h3 class="text-justify  text-accent text-2xl min-h-[4rem] flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <%= icon("code", class: "w-6 h-6 text-accent ") %>
            Development
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-justify md:text-center text-gray-700">
            We have been developing Ruby on Rails applications since 2008 and are gradually adopting React for more dynamic interfaces.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 w-full md:text-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <h3 class="text-justify  text-accent text-2xl min-h-[4rem] flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <%= icon("handyman", class: "w-6 h-6  text-accent ") %>
            Maintenance
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-justify md:text-center text-gray-700">
            We ensure the maintenance of your Rails application by providing regular updates and bug fixes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 w-full md:text-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <h3 class="text-justify  text-accent text-2xl min-h-[4rem] flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <%= icon("integration", class: "w-6 h-6 text-accent ") %>
            Integration
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-justify md:text-center text-gray-700">
            Need to automate or connect different systems? We support you in integrating your tools.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 w-full md:text-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <h3 class="text-justify  text-accent text-2xl min-h-[4rem] flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <%= icon("design", class: "w-6 h-6 text-accent ") %>
            UX/UI Design          
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-justify md:text-center text-gray-700">
            We design intuitive user experiences and create functional prototypes tailored to your needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="footer-wave">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 62" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="
      M0,62
      Q300,2 600,32
      Q900,62 1200,32
      L1200,62
      L0,62
      Z
    " fill="#1f1f3d"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <section id="secteurs" class="w-full px-10 py-20 md:p-20 bg-info">
    <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl text-center text-white  mb-12">
      Our tools and <span class="text-gradient">areas of expertise</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-16">
      <div class="bg-white h-full border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:mx-4">
          <%= image_tag 'logos/rails_logo.avif', class: 'h-50 w-50', alt: 'Ruby on Rails Logo' %>
          <h3 class="text-center text-accent text-2xl mt-2 mb-4">Ruby on Rails</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="px-4">
          Ruby on Rails (RoR) is an open-source web framework based on Ruby, known for its speed of development and reliability.
          <br>
          <br>
          Used by major companies such as Airbnb, Shopify, GitHub, Twitch, SoundCloud, Coinbase, and Heroku.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white h-full border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:mx-4">
          <%= image_tag 'logos/agile.svg', class: 'h-50 w-50', alt: 'Agile methodology symbol' %>
          <h3 class=" text-accent text-center text-2xl mt-2 mb-4">Agile</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="px-4">
          This approach is a flexible and iterative project management method focused on collaboration and continuous improvement.
          <br>
          <br>
          It helps reduce development time, optimize costs, and quickly adapt to changing requirements.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white h-full border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:mx-4">
          <%= image_tag "logos/mistral.avif", class: 'h-50 w-50', alt: 'Mistral' %>
          <h3 class=" text-accent text-center text-2xl mt-2 mb-4">AI and Machine Learning</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="px-4">
          We integrate AI solutions tailored to your needs, whether embedded in your platform or via external services.
          <br>
          <br>
          We work with advanced models such as Mistral and Gemini to build high-performance and innovative solutions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="footer-wave">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 60" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="
      M0,0
      Q300,60 600,30
      Q900,0 1200,30
      L1200,0
      L0,0
      Z
    " fill="#1f1f3d"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <section class="px-6 md:px-20 pb-20 pt-10">
    <h2 class="text-accent text-left mb-6 font-medium text-2xl uppercase tracking-wider">
      They trust us
    </h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-16">
      <div id="confiance" class="flex-1">
        <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col border border-gray-100">
          <%= icon("quote", class: "w-6 h-6 mb-4 text-left text-accent ") %></i>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-justify leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
          Philippe Nougaillon provides sustainable and reliable solutions and prioritizes simplicity in his development approach.
          A strong advocate of frugal innovation, he delivers original, robust, and well-adapted solutions.
          He is attentive and highly pedagogical in agile methodologies.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 border-t pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
          <div>
            <%= link_to "https://www.linkedin.com/in/philippe-eynaud-3a3ab835/", class: "flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium text-accent " do %>
              <%= icon("linkedin", class: "w-6 h-6 ") %> Philippe EYNAUD
            <% end %>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">
              Professor of Management Sciences at IAE Paris.
              <br>
              Author of
              <%= link_to "'The Management of Information Systems in Its Complexity'", 
                          "https://www.amazon.fr/management-syst%C3%A8me-dinformation-dans-complexit%C3%A9/dp/1784055026/ref=sr_1_5?qid=1687595735", 
                          class: "link italic no-underline", target: '_blank' %>. (2018) ISTE Editions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <%= image_tag "logos/iaelogo.avif", class: "h-10 w-auto opacity-80", alt: "IAE Paris Logo" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="confiance2" class="flex-1">
      <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col border border-gray-100">
        <%= icon("quote", class: "w-6 h-6 mb-4 text-left text-accent ") %></i>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-justify leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
        I had the pleasure of working with the Aïkku team on the deployment of the Planning-IAE tool.
        What a great experience! The Aïkku team embodies the "user orientation" I teach my students.
        Attentive and collaborative, they effectively translate user needs into concrete solutions.
        A smooth and efficient collaboration that I highly recommend.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 border-t pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
        <div>
          <%= link_to "https://www.linkedin.com/in/marieevelaporte/", class: "flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium text-accent " do %>
            <%= icon("linkedin", class: "w-6 h-6 ") %> Marie-Eve LAPORTE
          <% end %>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">
            Professor, Innovation Management & Future of Healthcare
          </p>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag "logos/iaelogo.avif", class: "h-10 w-auto opacity-80", alt: "IAE Paris Logo" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="p-0 mb-20 ">
  <div class="text-center mx-auto mb-20 px-4">
    <h2 class=" text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-accent mt-20">
      Our development process
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 text-lg">
      We support you at every stage, from idea to deployment,
      <br>
      with a user-centered approach.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 top-0 h-full w-1 bg-gray-200"></div>
    <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center mb-8">
      <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold shadow">
        1
      </div>
      <div class="ml-16 md:ml-0 md:w-1/2 md:pr-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-4 text-accent text-xl">
            <%= icon("discover", class: "w-6 h-6 mb-2 text-accent ") %>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-xl mb-3">Discover</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-justify">
            Analysis of your needs and environment, and definition of a tailored MVP for your business.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center mb-8">
      <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold shadow">
        2
      </div>
      <div class="ml-16 md:ml-auto md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-4 text-accent text-xl">
            <%= icon("creation", class: "w-6 h-6 mb-2 text-accent ") %>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-xl mb-3">MVP</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-justify">
            Rapid creation of a first functional version to validate the foundations of the project.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center mb-8">
      <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold shadow">
        3
      </div>
      <div class="ml-16 md:ml-0 md:w-1/2 md:pr-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-4 text-accent text-xl">
            <%= icon("build", class: "w-6 h-6 mb-2 text-accent ") %>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-xl mb-3">Build</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-justify">
            Agile cycles, user testing, and continuous improvement to refine the solution.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center mb-8">
      <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold shadow">
        4
      </div>
      <div class="ml-16 md:ml-auto md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-4 text-accent text-xl">
            <%= icon("deployer", class: "w-6 h-6 mb-2 text-accent ") %>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-xl mb-3">Deploy</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-justify">
            Production launch, team training, and onboarding support.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center mb-16">
      <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold shadow">
        5
      </div>
      <div class="ml-16 md:ml-0 md:w-1/2 md:pr-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-4 text-accent text-xl">
            <%= icon("evolution", class: "w-6 h-6 mb-2 text-accent ") %>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-xl mb-3">Maintain & evolve</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-justify">
            Support, continuous improvement, and adaptation to new needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center">
      <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 transform md:-translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold shadow">
        6
      </div>
      <div class="ml-16 md:ml-auto md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-4 text-accent text-xl">
            <%= icon("add", class: "w-6 h-6 mb-2 text-accent ") %>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-xl mb-3">Scale up</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-justify">
            Feature expansion, scaling, and performance optimization.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</div>